name: Gilbane Group
tag_list: cms, wcm, publishing, xml, enterprise-search, consulting, research
overview: Gilbane Group, a division of Outsell, Inc., provides analyst & consulting services focused on content technologies. Whether it involves web content management, multilingual content, enterprise search, enterprise social media, publishing, XML, XBRL, or related technologies, we can help you make vendor-neutral well-informed decisions. We also produce a variety of free content such as Research Reports, White Papers, Case Studies, Webinars, and more. Furthermore, we host 2 conferences annually in San Francisco & Boston which bring together some of the best and brightest thought leaders in the Content Technology world.
